# C++ Makefile Targets

## Requirement

All Makefiles for C++ projects SHALL provide `format` and `lint` targets.

The `format` target SHALL use clang-format to format all C++ source files.

The `lint` target SHALL run clang-tidy, cppcheck, and cpplint on all C++ source files.

